* OVERVIEW
This is a trivia-like-contest web application developed using meteor. Logged users can add trivia quiestions and answer tivia questions not posted by themself. All questions has 4 possible answers where only one is correct.

* INSTALL
Refer to http://docs.meteor.com/#quickstart for installing Meteor.

Packages needed:
- accounts-ui
- accounts-password
- bootstrap